name: Emperor Norton: Patron Saint of Crypto
description:
Emperor Norton in 1859 proclaimed himself "Norton I., Emperor of the United States" and shortly after declared he was "Protector of Mexico". He was a visionary and prophet who declared a tunnel be built between Oakland and San Francsico with multiple other declarations that came true. He made his own money which was accepted at most businesses in San Francisco, which is why through the power granted to me through Erisian Popes I - Empress Trash - declare he is the "Patron Saint of Crypto."
Minted and ratified in celebration of Miami Art Week 2021
10,000 were originally minted in honor of the 10,000 people who showed up to Emperor Nortons Funeral. // @EmpressTrash
